10 REM ================================
20 REM   MINI TEXT ADVENTURE
30 REM   CUPERTINO QUEST
40 REM ================================
50 HOME
60 PRINT "** CUPERTINO QUEST **"
70 PRINT
80 PRINT "THE YEAR IS 1976."
90 PRINT "YOU ARE IN A GARAGE IN"
100 PRINT "LOS ALTOS, CALIFORNIA."
110 PRINT
120 PRINT "YOUR MISSION: BUILD THE"
130 PRINT "FIRST APPLE COMPUTER."
140 PRINT
150 DIM IT(5)
160 LET SC = 0
170 LET RM = 1
180 REM -- ROOM DISPATCH --
190 ON RM GOTO 1000,2000,3000,4000,5000
200 PRINT "YOU SEEM LOST.": END
210 REM ================================
220 REM   SUBROUTINES
230 REM ================================
