1050 PRINT
1060 PRINT "WORKBENCH COVERED IN"
1070 PRINT "SCHEMATICS. A SOLDERING"
1080 PRINT "IRON GLOWS WARM."
1090 PRINT
1100 IF IT(1) = 0 THEN PRINT "A CIRCUIT BOARD SITS"
