1130 PRINT "EXITS: (E)AST TO HOUSE"
1140 PRINT "       (S)OUTH TO FLEA MARKET"
1150 PRINT
1160 GOSUB 500
1170 PRINT "WHAT DO YOU DO?"
1180 PRINT "(G)RAB, (E)AST, (S)OUTH ";
